nix_direnv_manual_reload

watch_file wrappers/default.nix
watch_file wrappers/**/*

watch_file various/npins/sources.json

watch_file packages.nix
watch_file various/packages/*
watch_file various/packages/**/*

# New nix-direnv version has a ton of unnecessary log spam. Made a comment
# complaining here: https://github.com/nix-community/nix-direnv/pull/627#issuecomment-3904824296
use nix &> /dev/null
